OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772019654
OL,3,CMan arrested after reports men entered
OL,4,Cmosque 'carrying multiple weapons'
OL,6,FA man has been arrested after reports
OL,7,Ftwo men entered a Mosque "carrying
OL,8,Fmultiple weapons" including a hammer
OL,9,Fand a knife as people worshipped
OL,10,Fduring Ramadan.
OL,12,FPolice were called to Manchester
OL,13,FCentral Mosque, on Upper Park Road, at
OL,14,Faround 8.40pm on 24 February after
OL,15,Freceiving a call about the two men
OL,16,F"acting suspiciously".
OL,18,FA statement from the mosque said
OL,19,Fvolunteers "spotted a suspicious bag"
OL,20,Fbefore approaching and challenging one
OL,21,Fof the men.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
