PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772019654
OL,3,CMan arrested after reports men entered
OL,4,Cmosque 'carrying multiple weapons'
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) said a
OL,7,Fman in his 40s has been arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of carrying an offensive
OL,9,Fweapon and possession of class B
OL,10,Fdrugs, and remains in custody for
OL,11,Fquestioning.
OL,13,FA search is underway to locate a
OL,14,Fsecond man.
OL,16,FNo threats were made and nobody was
OL,17,Finjured, the force added.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
