OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772019654
OL,3,CMan arrested after reports men entered
OL,4,Cmosque 'carrying multiple weapons'
OL,6,FIn a statement Manchester Central
OL,7,FMosque said "Mosque volunteers spotted
OL,8,Fthe suspicious bag containing an axe,
OL,9,Fwhich was placed into the main hall"
OL,10,Fbefore volunteers "escorted" a man
OL,11,Finto another room and found "multiple
OL,12,Fweapons including a hammer and a
OL,13,Fknife".
OL,15,FA second man left before officers
OL,16,Farrived, the Mosque added, and all
OL,17,FCCTV has been provided to police.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
