PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772019654
OL,3,CMan arrested after reports men entered
OL,4,Cmosque 'carrying multiple weapons'
OL,6,FSuperintendent Simon Nasim of City of
OL,7,FManchester Central district said: "We
OL,8,Fhave swiftly arrested one individual
OL,9,Fand officers are working to locate the
OL,10,Fsecond man. No threats were made and
OL,11,Fthankfully, no one was injured.
OL,13,F"You may notice an increased presence
OL,14,Fof patrols in the area while our
OL,15,Fenquiries continue. Please feel free
OL,16,Fto chat with our officers and let them
OL,17,Fknow your concerns.
OL,26,@oD@cOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
