OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772019654
OL,3,CMan arrested after reports men entered
OL,4,Cmosque 'carrying multiple weapons'
OL,6,F"There's no place for weapons on our
OL,7,Fstreets and we are committed to ensure
OL,8,Fall our communities feel safe to
OL,9,Fworship in peace and go about their
OL,10,Fdaily lives without fear.
OL,12,F"Anyone committing such offences will
OL,13,Fbe dealt with in accordance with the
OL,14,Flaw."
OL,16,FOfficers are appealing for witnesses
OL,17,Fto help with enquiries and have asked
OL,18,Fanyone with information to contact GMP
OL,19,Fon 101 or via the LiveChat function on
OL,20,Four website.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
